#\#CIF_2.0
# Tests: schema-less ingestion of scalar tags. All tags go to _cif_fallback
# regardless of content. _block_id must be 'test_fallback_scalars'. No structured
# tables should contain any rows. value_type for bare-word strings is 'string'.
# Dictionary: none (schema-less)

data_test_fallback_scalars
_sample.name          iron_oxide
_sample.description   'a reddish powder'
_measurement.temp     298
_measurement.pressure 1.0
_result.quality       high
_result.number        "11"
